-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/garden/garden-ideas/10-brilliant-garden-layout-ideas-to-help-create-your-dream-outdoor-space-308673\"\u003e\u003cu\u003egarden layout\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e. The colours also compliant your flower beds - especially pastel coloured peonies, hydrangeas and roses.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-Mt8wuPrWQEge7KvUBgpgTc\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘You can style pastel pieces with crisp white cushions for a clean, coastal feel, or layer with patterned textiles, lanterns, and vintage pots for a more eclectic look, so whatever the style of your garden, there is a pastel hue to suit,’ says Lena Gierasinska, Head of Product \u0026amp; Displays at\u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://barkerandstonehouse.sjv.io/c/221109/1016293/13315?subId1=idealhome-gb-1082336189707286261\u0026amp;sharedId=idealhome-gb\u0026amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barkerandstonehouse.co.uk%2F\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" data-url=\"https://www.barkerandstonehouse.co.uk/\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"hawklinks\" data-placeholder-url=\"https://barkerandstonehouse.sjv.io/c/221109/1016293/13315?subId1=hawk-custom-tracking\u0026amp;sharedId=hawk-prefix\u0026amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barkerandstonehouse.co.uk%2F\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"Barker \u0026amp; Stonehouse\" data-merchant-id=\"201665\" data-merchant-network=\"ImpactRad\" data-merchant-url=\"barkerandstonehouse.co.uk\"\u003e\u003cu\u003e Barker and Stonehouse\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘If you naturally shy away from colour and lean towards neutral hues, a bistro set in muted sage is a great way to incorporate this trend on a smaller scale.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePastel garden furniture offers an effortless way to inject personality into your outdoor living area. As for longevity, we see pastels continuing to evolve with changing tastes. While bold or neon colours can date quickly, pastels are soft and muted enough to remain timeless with the right styling.’\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"section-alternatives\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAlternatives\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eQVC isn\u0026#39;t the only brand getting in on the pastel garden furniture trend like we said, here are a few other pieces we\u0026#39;ve spotted.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv data-id=\"e5cd2aef-bfb2-4bbc-ade3-4d7e30f51d22\"\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://diy.pxf.io/c/221109/1632830/18948?subId1=idealhome-gb-2300476352788710156\u0026amp;sharedId=idealhome-gb\u0026amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.diy.com%2Fdepartments%2Fharbour-housewares-2-seater-sussex-bistro-set-round-yellow%2F5055512126736_BQ.prd%3Fsrsltid%3DAfmBOoqEQgPQjnKFn-keH9fe-D0_TxVogj2gVlFCjk6zs_PiwFz1mUQiZHs%26gQT%3D1\" data-model-name=\"Harbour Housewares 2 Seater Sussex Bistro Set - Round - Yellow\" data-url=\"https://www.diy.com/departments/harbour-housewares-2-seater-sussex-bistro-set-round-yellow/5055512126736_BQ.prd?srsltid=AfmBOoqEQgPQjnKFn-keH9fe-D0_TxVogj2gVlFCjk6zs_PiwFz1mUQiZHs\u0026amp;gQT=1\" target=\"_blank\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" data-hl-processed=\"hawklinks\" data-placeholder-url=\"https://diy.pxf.io/c/221109/1632830/18948?subId1=hawk-custom-tracking\u0026amp;sharedId=hawk-prefix\u0026amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.diy.com%2Fdepartments%2Fharbour-housewares-2-seater-sussex-bistro-set-round-yellow%2F5055512126736_BQ.prd%3Fsrsltid%3DAfmBOoqEQgPQjnKFn-keH9fe-D0_TxVogj2gVlFCjk6zs_PiwFz1mUQiZHs%26gQT%3D1\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"B\u0026amp;Q\" data-merchant-id=\"299090\" data-merchant-network=\"ImpactRad\" data-merchant-url=\"diy.com\"\u003e\u003cp data-bordeaux-i